  "home.achievements.card1Body": "255+ recorded public welfare live broadcasts; 800+ broadcast hours; TikTok pushed to 70,000+ highly relevant visitors; 1,200+ in-depth interviews.\n\nAmong them:\n\nIn-depth communication with 400+ attached **spirits (ghosts)**.\n\nHelped 240+ patients with mental disorders quickly relieve the suffering caused by attached **spirits (ghosts)** on-site.",
  "home.achievements.card1Title": "PRCASG super power achievement",
  "home.achievements.card2Body": "The achievements in the live broadcast were filmed into the second season of the documentary 'Woos Spirit Medicine.'\n1. Statistics on the survival status of **spirits (ghosts)** in the United States.\n2. Especially interesting and valuable **spirit (ghost)** cases.\n3. Cases of master spirit members of SMSC appearing in the live broadcast.\n4. Special cases in the spiritual realm, such as doctors and hospitals, and situations where cult members are specially attached.",
  "home.achievements.card2Title": "Truth Revealed of the spiritual realm",
  "home.achievements.cta": "View full content",
  "home.achievements.ctaIntro": "",
