  "home.achievements.kickerMetrics": "",
  "home.achievements.lead": "ASRA Founder Caros Woo used PRCASG superpowers in 2025 to systematically communicate with the **spirits (ghosts)** on American patients with mental disorders through TikTok live broadcasts, revealing the true living conditions of American **spirits (ghosts)**, and quickly help patients in the live room improve various diseases and disorders caused by attached **spirits (ghosts)**.",
