  "home.intro.ASRABody": "Spirit Realm's Ambassador are composed of tens of thousands of ordinary humans spread across various countries and ethnic groups around the world. Association members all possess the special power to remotely control attached spirits (ghosts) via the Internet (Power of Remote Controlling Attached Spirit (ghost) --- PRCASG); they are also tasked with the mission of revealing the truth of the Spiritual World to all of humanity.",
  "home.intro.ASRAFull": "Association of Spirit Realm's Ambassador",
  "home.intro.ASRAName": "ASRA",
  "home.intro.asraBody": "Spirit Realm's Ambassador are composed of tens of thousands of ordinary humans spread across various countries and ethnic groups around the world. Association members all possess the special power to remotely control attached spirits (ghosts) via the Internet (Power of Remote Controlling Attached Spirit (ghost) --- PRCASG); they are also tasked with the mission of revealing the truth of the Spiritual World to all of humanity.",
  "home.intro.asraFull": "Association of Spirit Realm's Ambassador",
  "home.intro.asraName": "ASRA",
  "home.intro.badge": "ASRA",
  "home.intro.learnMore": "✦   Full Organization Introduction   ✦",
  "home.intro.overviewAfter": "In the physical world, the New Era of UMMA Organization has under its jurisdiction the Association of Spirit Realm's Ambassador (ASRA);\nMembers of ASRA are human beings in the physical world. \n——In the spiritual world, the New Era of UMMA Organization has under its jurisdiction the Society of Master Spirit Controllers (SMSC); \nMembers of SMSC are senior master spirits in the spiritual world. \n**This website is the official website of ASRA.** \nThe New Era of UMMA Organization and SMSC do not maintain any websites in the physical world.",
  "home.intro.overviewBefore": "The New Era of UMMA Organization is the first one",
  "home.intro.overviewHighlight": "-----Spanning both the spiritual realm and the physical world",
  "home.intro.physicalWorld": "Physical World",
  "home.intro.smscBody": "The spiritual world has various types of master spirits. Among them, some are specifically responsible for helping ASRA members acquire the PRCASG superpower to control **spirits (ghosts)**; they are called controllers among the master spirits. The spiritual world has specifically established associations to train and coordinate tens of thousands of master spirits to become controllers, in order to effectively connect with and assist ASRA members",
  "home.intro.smscFull": "Society of Master Spirit Controllers",
  "home.intro.smscName": "SMSC",
  "home.intro.spiritRealm": "Spirit Realm",
  "home.intro.subtitle": "New Era of UMMA Organization",
  "home.intro.title": "What is The New Era of \nUMMA Organization?",
  "home.join.body": "Become a member of the Ambassador of Spirit Realm Association. You are not only saving yourself from mental disorders. More importantly, you gain the PRCASG superpower to save others, a profession that will never be replaced by AI.",
  "home.join.cta": "✦   Visit: Join Us   ✦",
  "home.join.subtitle": "The identity of an ambassador is not just about honor",
  "home.join.title": "Learn & Join",
  "home.truth.abstractBody": "As the founder of ASRA, Woos family filmed a series of three-season documentaries of spirit life and world for over 1,400 minutes. This documentary is the first time in human history to systematically explore and reveal the truth of **spirit **life, world and governor with a large amount of evidence",
  "home.truth.abstractHeading": "The Truth We Found",
  "home.truth.s1.cta": "Explore Season I",
  "home.truth.s1.description": "Collecting all true scientific research materials from East and West regarding **spirit (soul)**, PSI, NDE, past-life memories, and other topics related to **spirit (soul)** and the Ethereal Realm. With personal possession, supernatural and spirit-exorcism experiences.",
  "home.truth.s1.season": "SEASON 1",
  "home.truth.s1.title": "Woos Record of Soul",
  "home.truth.s2.cta": "Explore Season II",
  "home.truth.s2.description": "This documentary provides, from a scientific perspective, evidence that **spirit (soul**) and **spirits (ghosts)** exist both before and after death, and shows how they can cause illness in the physical body—the organs, physiological systems, and basic pathology involved. It contains four parts: \n(1) Evidence for **spirits (ghosts)** and their general situation. \n(2) Physiology of the human **spirit (soul)**. \n(3) Pathology of the human **spirit (soul)**. \n(4) Physiology and pathology of **spirits (ghosts)**.",
  "home.truth.s2.season": "SEASON 2",
  "home.truth.s2.title": "Woos Spirit Medicine",
  "home.truth.s3.cta": "Explore Season III",
  "home.truth.s3.description": "The management authority of the master spirit is given by the superiors layer after layer. The ultimate superior is UMMA. The spiritual realm and our 13 billion-year-old real universe are not natural products, but are created by the creator --UMMA. His **spirit (soul)** control system and team control the consciousness of human free will, the evolution of life on earth and the ultimate fate of human civilization",
  "home.truth.s3.season": "SEASON 3",
  "home.truth.s3.title": "Universal Matrix of Meta Awareness--The creator",
